New York City Area Is Under Tornado Watch Until 8 P.M. as Storms Move In

-- B y   C h a r l o t t e   P o r t e r
-- 
2011-06-01T17:51:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-01/new-york-city-area-is-under-tornado-watch-until-8-p-m-as-storms-move-in.html
The New York City area and parts of
the Northeast from  Pennsylvania  to  Maine  are under a tornado
watch as severe thunderstorms move through the region, the
 National Weather Service  said.  The watch for New York, northern  New Jersey  and southern
Connecticut is in effect until 8 p.m.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Charlotte Porter at 
 cporter11@bloomberg.net  